---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Volunteer"
  description="Volunteer with MCLA and help make a difference for the mantle cell lymphoma community. Multiple opportunities available."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-primary/5 via-warm-white to-sage/20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Volunteer With MCLA</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-charcoal/60 leading-relaxed">
        Your time and skills can help us reach more patients and families. Here's how you can contribute.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          MCLA is a growing organization, and volunteers are essential to our success. Whether you're a patient, caregiver, medical professional, or someone who wants to support the MCL community, we have opportunities for you.
        </p>

        <h2>Volunteer Opportunities</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 not-prose my-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-sage p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Patient & Caregiver Mentors</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Share your experience with newly diagnosed patients and caregivers. Provide peer support and guidance to help others navigate their MCL journey.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-sage p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Content & Communications</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Help create patient education materials, write blog posts, manage social media, or contribute to our newsletter. Writers, editors, and designers are welcome.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-sage p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Community Outreach</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Help us connect with patients, support groups, and healthcare providers in your community. Be a local ambassador for MCLA.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-sage p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Event Support</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Assist with planning and executing educational events, fundraisers, and awareness campaigns — both virtual and in-person.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-sage p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Professional Skills</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Contribute professional expertise in areas like legal, finance, technology, marketing, healthcare, or nonprofit management.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>How to Get Started</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70">
          Ready to volunteer? Fill out our contact form and let us know your interests and availability. We'll match you with opportunities that fit your skills and schedule.
        </p>

        <div class="not-prose mt-8">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-7 py-3 bg-teal-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-dark transition-colors no-underline"
          >
            Sign Up to Volunteer
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
